info.author: LIU Yu
info.description:
PyUUID is a python package for generating RFC4122 universally unique 
identifiers (uuid). It is currently implemented upon the uuid library 
distributed with the e2fsprogs project, and can generate version 1 (time-based) 
and 4 (random-based) uuid's.
